.RS 4
The empty string\&. It will always have Id 1\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBSYSTEM_SYSTEM "system:system"\fR
.RS 4
The name of the always installed "system" solvable\&.
.RE
.SH "SOLVABLE ATTRIBUTES"
.sp
