.RE
.PP
\fBREPOSITORY_LOCATION "repository:location"\fR
.RS 4
This is used to provide a file name in the stub\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBREPOSITORY_ADDEDFILEPROVIDES "repository:addedfileprovides"\fR
